data.description: Expansive open concept ranch with just under 2700 square feet on the first floor plus a finished basement with a 2nd fireplaced, wet bar, exercise room.  Great for entertaining, plus there is still a ton of room for storage.  The first floor includes an enormous kitchen island with a solid surface counter and tons of cabinets plus a walk in pantry.  Cathedral ceiling in the living room with a gas fireplace.  Oversized master BR, walk in closet and private bath.  4 season room with hot tub plus a relaxing 3 season screened porch area.  Updates include roof, gutters, furnace and AC, water softener, water heater, hot tub maintenance, and more.  Private 3 acre parcel.
